- type() is triangle iff nr_of_sides() is 3.
- type() is quadrilateral iff nr_of_sides() is 4.
- (nr_of_vertices() is 3 iff nr_of_sides() is 3) and (nr_of_vertices() is 4 iff nr_of_sides() is 4).
- nr_of_sides() is 3 is a sufficient condition for convex().
- convex() iff (for every n ∈ Side_Nr, it is true that angle(n) < 180).
- equilateral() iff (for every n ∈ Side_Nr, it is true that length(n) is length(1) or length(n) is 0).
- nr_of_sides() is 3 is a sufficient condition for subtype() is right_triangle or subtype() is regular_triangle or subtype() is irregular.
- nr_of_sides() is 4 is a sufficient condition for subtype() is square or subtype() is rectangle or subtype() is irregular.
- subtype() is square or subtype() is rectangle is a sufficient condition for nr_of_sides() is 4.
- subtype() is regular_triangle iff nr_of_sides() is 3 and equilateral().
- subtype() is regular_triangle iff nr_of_sides() is 3 and (for every n ∈ Side_Nr, it is true that angle(n) is 60 or angle(n) is 0).
- subtype() is right_triangle iff nr_of_sides() is 3 and (there is a n ∈ Side_Nr such that angle(n) is 90).
- nr_of_sides() is 4 and ¬(subtype() = irregular) iff (for every n ∈ Side_Nr, it is true that angle(n) is 90 or angle(n) is 0).
- subtype() is rectangle is a sufficient condition for length(3) is length(1) and length(2) is length(4) and ¬(length(2) = length(1)).
- subtype() is square is a sufficient condition for nr_of_sides() is 4 and equilateral().
- type() is triangle is a sufficient condition for (length(1) ≤ length(2) + length(3)) and (length(2) ≤ length(3) + length(1)) and (length(3) ≤ length(1) + length(2)).
- perimeter() is the sum of length(n) for all n ∈ Side_Nr.
- the sum of angle(n) for all n ∈ Side_Nr is (nr_of_sides() - 2) ⨯ 180.
- for every x ∈ Side_Nr, it is true that 0 ≤ length(x).
- for every x ∈ Side_Nr, it is true that 0 ≤ angle(x).
- for every x ∈ Side_Nr, it is true that ¬(angle(x) = 180).
- for every n ∈ Side_Nr, it is true that angle(n) is 0 iff nr_of_vertices() < n.
- for every n ∈ Side_Nr, it is true that length(n) is 0 iff nr_of_sides() < n.
